      "message": "The original apk openjdk11-jre added on /usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk, but onap/integration-java11 image has JAVA_HOME on /opt/java/openjdk. Several startup scripts, for example policy-api.sh has JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk/ hard coded. if we do not want to make a sym link, then we need to scan/change all scripts again.",
